description: A very nervous Pierce Paris is anxiously awaiting to audition for a final callback with Masqulin. His supportive boyfriend has even accompanied him to… help ease his worries. It’s down to himself and one other model, the cocky and boastful Igor Romani, who seems confident that he will be the “winner” in this scenario. Once they are before the panel, the models use a variety of methods to prove that they are the better choice for Masqulin. It’s going to be a fight to the finish, or maybe a bang!
title: COMPETITIVE STREAK: Pierce Paris and Igor Romani RAW
